    "internal_collapsed_note": "The 31 entries are the user-facing monitors. Internal sub-containers (mailcow ~18, *-db/*-redis, mcp-*, sidecars) are NOT in Kuma; for the collapsed 'Belső szolgáltatások' use `docker ps -a` MINUS the docker_name values below.",
    "uptime_pct_note": "Kuma /metrics has monitor_response_time (latency) but NO uptime%. v1: show latency, uptime%=null. If uptime% is required, poll the Kuma socket.io API (uptime-kuma-api, creds vault:KUMA_ADMIN_USER/PASS) on a SLOW cadence (e.g. hourly) -> NOT in the 15s hot path.",
    "open_items": [
      "No 'Uptime Kuma' self-monitor (Kuma can't reliably monitor itself). FORGE derives Kuma=up from a successful /metrics fetch.",
      "AdGuard/IPFS/Obsidian/Paperless have admin UIs (8093/5001/8070/8050) but are null per spec '*' -> flip webui_url to enable links."
    ]
  },
